---
import { site } from '../data/site';
import TechIcon from './icons/TechIcon.astro';
---

<section id="contacto" class="reveal mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16">
	<h2 class="font-mono text-sm text-accent-2">06. Contacto</h2>

	<h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-fg md:text-3xl">
		Disponible para nuevas oportunidades
	</h3>
	<p class="mt-3 max-w-xl text-fg/90">
		Estoy abierto a evaluar oportunidades en desarrollo backend y fullstack. Si
		buscas sumar a tu equipo experiencia en sistemas estables y buenas prácticas,
		escríbeme o revisa mi CV.
	</p>

	<div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
		<a
			href={`mailto:${site.email}`}
			class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-primary px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-primary-fg transition-transform hover:scale-[1.02]"
		>
			<TechIcon slug="gmail" label="Email" class="size-5 bg-white/90" />
			{site.email}
		</a>
		<a
			href={site.cvHref}
			download
			class="rounded-md border border-border px-4 py-2 text-sm text-fg transition-colors hover:border-accent-2 hover:text-accent-2"
		>
			Descargar CV
		</a>
		<a
			href={site.linkedin}
			target="_blank"
			rel="noopener noreferrer"
			class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-border px-4 py-2 text-sm text-fg transition-colors hover:border-accent-2 hover:text-accent-2"
		>
			<TechIcon slug="linkedin" label="LinkedIn" class="size-5" />
			LinkedIn
		</a>
		<a
			href={site.github}
			target="_blank"
			rel="noopener noreferrer"
			class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-border px-4 py-2 text-sm text-fg transition-colors hover:border-accent-2 hover:text-accent-2"
		>
			<TechIcon slug="github" label="GitHub" class="size-5 bg-white/90" />
			GitHub
		</a>
	</div>
</section>
